Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My homework for home economics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to finish this apron by tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun! So-unds fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's fun about it, you...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fun, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:17.34,Sign,,0,0,110,,{\fade(1500,2000)\c&HDBC9B6&\3c&H3D0100&\3a&H39&\bord5\blur5}Episode 77 \N{\fs35}Calling on Hardworking Pixiervants! {必殺シゴト人参上!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone—you've finished it, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who didn't bring it today \Ncan still bring their homework tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you... {/such thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, well... Here, see? Mine's not even half-done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same for everyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we could finish it \Nearlier than tomorrow anyway. Right, Jabao?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I've finished mine already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"Jaba!" There.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:02:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako, you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the World Junior Sewing Contest winner, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Korekiyo, you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sewing an apron is like taking a candy from a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I had so much more time to spare, \NI even made potholders! {/got tired of waiting}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The amazing one here is Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She also made a pillow, a stuffed toy, a pajama, and a dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I really think it's nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What even is this apron, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You say it's half-done, \Nbut really, it's as though you haven't even started yet! {/not done at all}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! {maybe saying "you're a liar [honmaru]"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Jabao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here! Give it back! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he even thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There really is no helping Honmaru's clumsiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happened, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In the whole class, \NI was the only one who couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone but me \Nhanded this homework in already! {no clue what he means: I'm the only one made to do this homework}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not being very attentive \Nto my true stories of woe! {lit: I'm telling the truth but you're sleeping}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru. I've just... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep already, Taru-kun! {unsure why questioning intonation}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sleep, but you do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Trunsform.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not coming out at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mom! Mom, please help! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I can't do this... {no clue what he means, mom you idiot?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Imbecile! Do your goddamn homework yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, don't even think about helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be that cruel?! {actually "angry" but idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I sewed it in the wrong spot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to square one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta... redo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleepy...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta do it somehow... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... If I don't finish it until tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ria!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I help you just today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Counting on you, Pixiervants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't finish the apron...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow at school... {g no clue what's last word}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, gotta do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Before tomorrow morning, let's finish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Before tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta do it, gotta do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I fell asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's 7:30! I'm screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the apron ready! \NWhat do I do? What do I do? What do I do? What...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The apron is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go pee, brush our teeth, and eat our meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, it was you? Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You finished the apron while I was sleeping! \NWith this... With this, I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Apron? Me not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Then, who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Pixiervants house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pixiervants?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Ria's smell on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! It was Ria, then? \NThank you, Sister Ria!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, these Pixiervants are mighty useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did a house produce an apron?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong, wrong! You wear it on head while sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, go pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Brush my teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat my meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Our meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Go pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Brush your teeth! Brush-brush your teeth! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat your meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh! Yummy, yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Honmaru? You've seen these four\Nfrom the house do my work for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are very responsible \Nand always bring the work to completion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:11:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But remember, Honmaru. \NPixiervants only work while you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. In order to get the job done, \NI have to spend that time sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's alright. I have Cloudrowsy.{nc, nemuke in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You tear this up and rub it into your head \Nto fall asleep amazingly anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did everyone submit \Ntheir homework for home economics today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, nicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:12:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, today's homework is a set of math problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. The range of problems are from page 65 \Nthrough page 134. I hope it's not too much for you.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it even possible to do that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This amount exceeds even the scope \Nof the World Junior Math Contest. {suspect "more than you have to solve at ..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, it's not too much for you, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Honmaru-kun, that's unusual for you. \NIt's due tomorrow, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am. You can do that much \Nif you try really hard. Right, Jabao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's make it page 65 through 134. {act. 135 but I think it's a typo, was still 134 in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A cakewalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! We didn't get a cut on\Nthe homework because of your nonsense! {/wasn't reduced}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao, don't you need to hurry home \Nto be able to do that homework in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Homework in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going home, Ryoguchiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Jaba-san, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, Taru-chan! \NWhy are you two still up? It's time to go to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm still not one bit sleepy. \NI can't get the Pixiervants to do their job this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, wanna use Cloudrowsy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's do that, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'm counting on you, dear Pixiervants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do a set of math problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Math homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Math homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta do it! Do it! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,First question, hm-hm.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,First question, hm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,First question, hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,First question, hm-hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,317 minus...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! We guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At math!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd have thought? {act. we were}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, did you do your math homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Super! Ah, you see, I forgot mine at home, \Nso could you show me yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Wouldn't that make \Nfor an interesting {usual }pattern reverse?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a matter of grave concern! \NHonmaru-sama, Honmaru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let us see it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys sure are hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they say we gotta help each over \Nat times of need. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God. And Honmaru-sama!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive! Every single one is correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, if you put your mind to it, \Nyou can really do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As a thank you, I think I should let Honmaru-kun \Ndo anything he wants with me. {/listen to whatever ... says}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, how about a... A kiss, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's gotten into me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's morning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still sleepy, Honmaru. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I wish I could sleep for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I wonder if my homework is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploy Cloudrowsy, quick!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's not waste any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, how long \Nhave I been waiting for this moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, Taru-chan, it's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to wake up, you two. \NYou'll be late for school. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Shoot! She's waking him up!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how cute! Are you friends of Taru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloudrowsy, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in our policy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To use whatever means necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To bring the work to the completion...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And not any other way! {act. "not being satisfied; not being able to enjoy"}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be safe all the way out here, {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is my breakf—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taruruuto! Flirting with Mimora-chan again, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished, finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Pixiervants!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's with everyone sleeping here, of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, it's 10 already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'm late, late, late...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I know I came to school late...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at this, Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done all of my math homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me \Nabout your math homework now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You skipped school for a week straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you show up \Nto tell me about your homework?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A week?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your act together! {shape up!; act properly!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts. It hurts, teacher! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Forgive me! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pixiervants are amazing! They worked on one set of math problems for a week straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have helped back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But perhaps, it'll at least teach you \Nnot to rely on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.55,0:22:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable! Jabao's continuous outrageous behavior... {behaving outrageously as though there were no one around; acting without consideration for others; arrogance; audacity; insolence​}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It falls upon me to punish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.93,0:22:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did he become a good guy all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Jabao became a good guy \Nafter eating the Good-Hearted Windowl. {心の真丼}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Jabao is suddenly becoming popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, give it to me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:22:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you mistook! That's Devil-Bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:02.70,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 78 \NGood Guy Jabao!? {善人!?じゃば夫}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.72,0:23:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun: \NGood Guy Jabao!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru scary!
